org.springframework.util.concurrent

接口 ListenableFutureCallback<T>

  • 类型参数:
    T - the result type
    所有超级接口:
    FailureCallback, SuccessCallback<T>

    public interface ListenableFutureCallback<T>
extends SuccessCallback<T>, FailureCallback
    Callback mechanism for the outcome, success or failure, from a ListenableFuture.
    从以下版本开始:
    4.0
    作者:
    Arjen Poutsma, Sebastien Deleuze

    • 方法概要

      • 从接口继承的方法 org.springframework.util.concurrent.SuccessCallback

        onSuccess

      • 从接口继承的方法 org.springframework.util.concurrent.FailureCallback

        onFailure
